Depending on your case, you will need 2 step studs: 8 x 6 for the cooler
bracket. Also you will need to remove the short 6mm stud from the case and put
a longer one in for the 3rd hole on the bracket. You will need the correct
step-down seals.
Here is a little info on the seals:
 http://www.oldvolkshome.com/oilcool.htm


